                                                            "by monitoring the sensor's response to a standard quinine "

                                                            "the sensor's physical or chemical environment.\n"
                                                            '\n'

                                                            'with the same sensor (intra-sensor reproducibility) or '
                                                            'across different sensors fabricated in the same way '
                                                            '(inter-sensor reproducibility). This is usually '
                                                            'quantified by the relative standard deviation (RSD) of '
                                                            "the sensor's response to a fixed quinine concentration "

                                                            'by low RSD values (typically <5%).\n'
